  "description": "This small resource pack replaces the flame, soul flame, and copper flame particles with animated versions.",
  "body": "# Better Flame Particles\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/Tschipcraft/better_flame_particles/stargazers\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/stars/Tschipcraft/better_flame_particles?logo=github&colorA=181712&colorB=fff5c6&style=for-the-badge\" title=\"GitHub stars\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/better-flame-particles\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/782814?logo=curseforge&label=CurseForge&colorA=181712&colorB=fff5c6&style=for-the-badge\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/Tschipcraft/better_flame_particles/releases/latest\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/Tschipcraft/better_flame_particles/total?logo=github&colorA=181712&colorB=fff5c6&style=for-the-badge\" title=\"GitHub downloads\"></a>\n\n> A resource pack for 1.14.x-26.2.x\n\n## Features\n\n_Witness mesmerizing animations as the flames dance and flicker._\n\nThis resource pack replaces the flame, soul flame, and copper flame particles with animated versions.\n\n\n## Preview\n<p>\n  <img alt=\"Animated Flame Particle\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tschipcraft/better_flame_particles/master/demo.gif\" style=\"image-rendering:crisp-edges\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\">\n  <img alt=\"Animated Soul Flame Particle\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tschipcraft/better_flame_particles/master/demo2.gif\" style=\"image-rendering:crisp-edges\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\">\n  <img alt=\"Animated Copper Flame Particle\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tschipcraft/better_flame_particles/master/demo3.gif\" style=\"image-rendering:crisp-edges\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\">\n</p>\n\n\n## Compatibility\n\nThis pack overrides the flame particles. Non-vanilla-style resource packs will look out of place with it.\n\n<img title=\"Supported Minecraft versions\" src=\"https://tschipo.alwaysdata.net/assets/supported?untested_versions=26.3&supported_versions=1.14,1.15,1.16,1.17,1.18,1.19,1.20,1.21,26.1,26.2&total_versions=%3C=1.13,1.14,1.15,1.16,1.17,1.18,1.19,1.20,1.21,26.1,26.2,26.3&progress_bar=false&mc_background=false&icons=true&platform=modrinth\">\n\n\n## External Links\n\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/better-flame-particles\">\n<img width=\"40px\" alt=\"CurseForge logo\" title=\"View Better Flame Particles on CurseForge\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tschipcraft/badges/main/assets/curseforge-modrinth.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/better-flame-particles/\">\n<img width=\"40px\" alt=\"PlanetMinecraft logo\" title=\"View Better Flame Particles on PlanetMinecraft\" src=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/images/layout/favicon-128.png\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/C0C5HEJB2\">\n<img width=\"250px\" title=\"Support me on Ko-fi\" src=\"https://storage.ko-fi.com/cdn/brandasset/kofi_button_red.png\">\n</a>\n\n\n## Partner Offers\n\nWant to buy **Hytale** or upgrade your edition? Use creator code `Tschipcraft` upon checkout for me to receive a commission! (The price for you stays the same)\n\n<a href=\"https://billing.sparkedhost.com/aff.php?aff=2611\">\n<img title=\"Support me by getting a server @ Sparked Host (This is an affiliate link)\" src=\"https://tschipo.alwaysdata.net/assets/partner/sparked_banner.png\">\n</a>",
